    <datacred>Funding and (or) support for this study were provided by the USGS Coastal and Marine Geology Program and the University of New Orleans. We thank R/V G.K. Gilbert captain Dave Bennett of the USGS in St. Petersburg, FL for his assistance in data collection. This document was improved by the reviews of Ellen Raabe (USGS) and Brendan Dwyer (Jacobs Technology Inc.) of the USGS in St. Petersburg, FL.</datacred>
